      • setHost

        public void setHost(java.lang.String hostName)
        Sets host name of the Contentstack.com Contentstack server.
        Parameters:
        hostName - host name.

        Note: Default hostname sets to cdn.contentstack.io and default protocol is HTTPS.

        Example :

         config.setHost("cdn.contentstack.io");

      • setSSL

        public void setSSL(boolean isSSL)
        Sets the protocol in base url.
        Parameters:
        isSSL - true/false values initiating calls (HTTPS/HTTP) respectively.

        Note: Default protocol is HTTPS.

        Example :

         config.setSSL(true);
